<topic template="Default" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>11.1.2 Machine without Reference Limit Switch (Butt Type Reference)</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">Machine without Reference Limit Switch (Butt Type Reference)</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Butt Type Reference method take reference with respect to the mechanical stopper.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text style="font-weight:bold;">Operation Procedure</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s)" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Select </text><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">[REFERENCE]</text><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;"> mode from the “Machine Mode Selection” switch.</text></li>
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Select the axis which reference position return need to be set.</text></li>
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Press the </text><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">[CYCLESTART]</text><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;"> button.</text></li>
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">The selected axis move towards the mechanical stopper in the direction that have been set in parameter at a constant feedrate.</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:65px;"><image src="Butt Type Reference 1.png" scale="38.00%" width="519" height="150" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:78px;"></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s)" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">The axis is butt against the mechanical stopper until the torque limit is set in.</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; margin-left:100px;"><image src="Butt Type Reference 2.png" scale="38.00%" width="513" height="146" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s)" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">After the axis butts the mechanical stopper the axis is retracted in opposite direction at the feed rate specified in parameter to the return distance specified in parameter.</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; margin-left:100px;"><image src="Butt Type Reference 3.png" scale="38.00%" width="513" height="162" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s)" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; page-break-before:always; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; page-break-before:always;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">From the return position the axis is again (second time) butt to the mechanical stopper in the direction set in parameter at constant feed rate.</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; margin-left:100px;"><image src="Butt Type Reference 4.png" scale="38.00%" width="516" height="147" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s)" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">After the axis butts the mechanical stopper the axis is retracted in opposite direction at the feed rate and distance specified in parameter.</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; margin-left:100px;"><image src="Butt Type Reference 5.png" scale="38.00%" width="516" height="175" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="1_11mm" style="text-align:center; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; margin-left:100px; page-break-before:always;"></para>
  </body>
